 href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/morm/8.2-3,6-7?lang=por#p2\">Mórm. 8:2–3, 6–7</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"12\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note12a\" data-full-marker=\"12a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124170721\" id=\"note12a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/lust-1?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Concupiscência</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"13\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note13a\" data-full-marker=\"13a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124170724\" id=\"note13a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/hel/3.16?lang=por#p16\">Hel. 3:16</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"14\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note14a\" data-full-marker=\"14a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124170726\" id=\"note14a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/9.24?lang=por#p24\">Morô. 9:24</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note14b\" data-full-marker=\"14b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124170729\" id=\"note14b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.1-3?lang=por#p1\">Morô. 1:1–3</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"15\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note15a\" data-full-marker=\"15a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124170731\" id=\"note15a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.10?lang=por#p10\">Al. 46:10</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/62.40?lang=por#p40\">62:40</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"16\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note16a\" data-full-marker=\"16a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124170733\" id=\"note16a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/1.7?lang=por#p7\">2 Né. 1:7</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/37.31?lang=por#p31\">Al. 37:3